author: Russell Brand
description:
The World Health Organization has positioned itself as the global authority on health—but who’s really pulling the strings? We unpack the explosive new revelations about the WHO’s private funding arm taking tens of millions in untraceable donations from Big Pharma, Big Tech, and anonymous sources. As unelected officials push sweeping global health regulations—vaccine passports, surveillance IDs, and lockdown powers—questions grow about the influence of corporate donors. With RFK Jr. and Trump rejecting WHO control, is this a turning point in the fight against globalized medical power?
